## Badges

Inline status badges for labeling features and API fields:

<p>
<Badge type="new" /> <Badge type="beta" /> <Badge type="deprecated" /> <Badge type="required" /> <Badge type="optional" /> <Badge type="default" />
</p>

Use badges inline with text: the `user.email` field is <Badge type="required" /> while `user.nickname` is <Badge type="optional" />. This endpoint is <Badge type="deprecated" />, use `/v2/users` instead.

Custom label: <Badge type="new">{#snippet children()}v2.1{/snippet}</Badge>

